--- Accessibility Improvements for Rules Index Page ---

The following improvements can be applied to enhance accessibility:

1. **Main Content Role**
   Add role="main" to the root div element

2. **Heading Structure**
   Add proper heading hierarchy with aria-level attributes

3. **Icon Accessibility**
   Add aria-hidden="true" to all decorative SVG icons

4. **Form Controls**
   - Add aria-label to select elements
   - Add aria-label to buttons without visible text
   - Add aria-describedby for form hints

5. **Interactive Elements**
   - Add aria-pressed for toggle buttons
   - Add aria-current="page" for active pagination
   - Add aria-label for star toggle buttons

6. **Loading States**
   Add role="status" aria-live="polite" for loading indicators

7. **Lists**
   - Add role="list" to rule containers
   - Add role="listitem" to individual rules

8. **Navigation**
   Add role="navigation" aria-label="ページネーション" to pagination

9. **Search Input**
   Add aria-label or connect to visible label

10. **Keyboard Navigation**
    The existing keyboard shortcuts are good, consider adding:
    - Focus management for modal/dropdown interactions
    - Skip links for keyboard users

Sample implementation for key areas:

```vue
<!-- Main container -->
<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-950" role="main">

<!-- Heading with proper level -->
<h1 class="heading-1 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2" role="heading" aria-level="1">

<!-- Decorative icons -->
<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">

<!-- Form controls -->
<select 
  v-model="filters.visibility"
  @change="fetchRules"
  class="..."
  aria-label="公開範囲フィルター"
>

<!-- Toggle buttons -->
<button
  @click="toggleTag(tag)"
  :aria-label="`タグ: ${tag} ${selectedTags.includes(tag) ? '(選択中)' : ''}`"
  :aria-pressed="selectedTags.includes(tag)"
>

<!-- Loading state -->
<div v-if="loading" role="status" aria-live="polite" aria-label="ルールを読み込み中">

<!-- Rule list -->
<div v-if="!loading && rules.length > 0" class="grid..." role="list">
  <div v-for="rule in rules" :key="rule.id" role="listitem">

<!-- Links with context -->
<NuxtLink
  :to="getRuleUrl(rule)"
  :aria-label="`${rule.name} - ${rule.description || '説明なし'}`"
>

<!-- Star button -->
<button
  @click.prevent="toggleStar(rule)"
  :aria-label="rule.isStarred ? 'スターを解除' : 'スターを付ける'"
  :aria-pressed="rule.isStarred"
>

<!-- Pagination -->
<div role="navigation" aria-label="ページネーション">
  <button
    v-for="page in visiblePages"
    :aria-label="`ページ ${page}`"
    :aria-current="page === currentPage ? 'page' : undefined"
  >
```

These improvements will ensure the rules index page is accessible to all users, including those using screen readers and keyboard navigation.